  <brief_title>QOL in Incarcerated Inguinal Hernias: TAPP Vs Open Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Comparison of the Quality of Life and Outcomes in Patient's With Incarcerated Inguinal Hernias: Laparoscopic Transabdominal Pre-peritoneal (TAPP) Versus Modified Lichtenstein Hernioplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
